title: The Artist Mission Part 3 isn't working
body: I got the 12 items part completed but the ward part stopped reacting. it's stuck on half completed and I placed wards in two different games controls and stealth wards. What gives?

replies.body:
Looks like someone was able to get that verified and completed for you already, sweetness!

{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
This happened to me too, you have to get a riot employee to pass the mission through once they can confirm that you legit did the mission and it's not reacting
